    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "^ Delta Air Lines\nWORLDWIDE TIMETABLE\nEffective October 1, 1996 - November 30, 1996\nSkymiles\nA Delta Airline\nSkyMiles\n3731 3213-5\n^ Delta Air Lines\nSkyMiles\nOPTIME\n3737 321345 61008\n^ Delta Air Lines\nSkyMiles\nVALB\n3737 321345\nB ATKINS\nOPTIMA\n61008\nAMERICAN\n^ Delta Air Lines\nSkyMiles\n3737 321349\nVAID\nOPTIMA\n61008\n96\nAMERICAN\nEXPRESS\nJ BAKIS\nNOT TRANSFERABLE\nStart Earning Sky Miles®\nFor Every Dollar You Spend.\nCall 1-800-SKY-MILE.\nFor more information, see application inside.",
